 ref="#pmb10860" type="person">Paula</rs></p><closer><anchor xml:id="T_L00560_1" type="textConst"/>Ihr<note xml:id="T_L00560_1h" type="textConst">am oberen Rand auf dem Kopf</note><signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div></body><back><listPerson><person xml:id="pmb2121">
